ygData.messageBody:
Its fun when you stumble on the wisp goldmine for the first time :).

West Commons and Zombie Island has quite afew of them to hunt. Be careful
they always seem to do more damage when there are two (whenever I fought one
they would hit for 1 or 2, as soon as two appeared they would start hitting
for 15. Weird).
